            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-0.5 text-accent-400">✓</span> Everything in Pro</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-0.5 text-accent-400">✓</span> Multi-location management</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-0.5 text-accent-400">✓</span> Cross-shop analytics</li>
