          </ul>
          <div class="mt-6">
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-2">Multi-shop pricing:</p>
            <div class="space-y-1 text-xs text-gray-400">
              <p>2 shops → <strong class="text-white">$44.99</strong>/mo</p>
              <p>3 shops → <strong class="text-white">$59.99</strong>/mo</p>
              <p>5 shops → <strong class="text-white">$89.99</strong>/mo</p>
